Epoch:  0 | Step:  1 | batch x:  [ 8.  5.] | batch y:  [ 3.  6.]
Epoch:  1 | Step:  0 | batch x:  [  3.   4.   2.   9.  10.   1.   7.   8.] | batch y:  [  8.   7.   9.   2.   1.  10.   4.   3.]
